trans-unit.source: Serves as the base class for classes that provides access to session-state values, session-level settings, and lifetime management methods.
trans-unit.target: 用作提供对会话状态值、会话级别设置和生存期管理方法的访问的类的基类。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateBase> class is an abstract class that contains the same members as the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState> class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateBase>类是一个抽象类，包含相同的成员<xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState>类。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateBase> class enables you to create derived classes that are like the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState> class, but that you can customize and that work outside the ASP.NET pipeline.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateBase>类使你能够创建类似的派生的类<xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState>类，但你可以自定义并使用 ASP.NET 管道外部。

trans-unit.source: When you perform unit testing, you typically use a derived class to implement members with customized behavior that fulfills the scenario you are testing.
trans-unit.target: 当执行单元测试时，通常使用派生的类以实现具有满足你测试的方案的自定义行为的成员。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateWrapper> class derives from the <xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateBase> class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateWrapper> 类是从 <xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateBase> 类派生的。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateWrapper> class serves as a wrapper for the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState> class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateWrapper>类用作包装器<xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState>类。

trans-unit.source: At run time, you typically use an instance of the <xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateWrapper> class to call members of the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState> object.
trans-unit.target: 在运行时，你通常使用的实例<xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateWrapper>类来调用的成员<xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState>对象。

trans-unit.source: Initializes the class for use by an inherited class instance.
trans-unit.target: 初始化该类供继承的类实例使用。

trans-unit.source: This constructor can only be called by an inherited class.
trans-unit.target: 此构造函数只能由继承的类调用。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, cancels the current session.
trans-unit.target: 当在派生类中被重写时，取消当前会话。

trans-unit.source: Always.
trans-unit.target: 始终。

trans-unit.source: The name of the item to add to the session-state collection.
trans-unit.target: 要添加到会话状态集合的项的名称。

trans-unit.source: The value of the item to add to the session-state collection.
trans-unit.target: 要添加到会话状态集合的项的值。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, adds an item to the session-state collection.
trans-unit.target: 当在派生类中被重写时，向会话状态集合添加一个项。

trans-unit.source: Always.
trans-unit.target: 始终。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, removes all keys and values from the session-state collection.
trans-unit.target: 在派生类中重写时，从会话状态集合中移除所有键和值。

trans-unit.source: Always.
trans-unit.target: 始终。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets or sets the character-set identifier for the current session.
trans-unit.target: 当在派生类中重写时，获取或设置当前会话的字符集标识符。

trans-unit.source: The character-set identifier for the current session.
trans-unit.target: 当前会话的字符集标识符。

trans-unit.source: Always.
trans-unit.target: 始终。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets a reference to the current session-state object.
trans-unit.target: 在派生类中重写时，获取对当前会话状态对象的引用。

trans-unit.source: The current session-state object.
trans-unit.target: 当前会话状态对象。

trans-unit.source: Always.
trans-unit.target: 始终。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets a value that indicates whether the application is configured for cookieless sessions.
trans-unit.target: 在派生类中重写时，获取一个值，该值指示是否为无 Cookie 会话配置应用程序。

trans-unit.source: One of the cookie-mode values that indicate whether the application is configured for cookieless sessions.
trans-unit.target: cookie-mode 值之一，指示是否为无 Cookie 会话配置应用程序。

trans-unit.source: Always.
trans-unit.target: 始终。

trans-unit.source: The array to copy session values to.
trans-unit.target: 要将会话值复制到的数组。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in <c>array</c> at which copying starts.
trans-unit.target: <c>array</c> 中从零开始的索引，在此处开始复制。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, copies the collection of session-state values to a one-dimensional array, starting at the specified index in the array.
trans-unit.target: 当在派生类中重写时，从数组中指定索引处开始，将会话状态值集合复制到一维数组。

trans-unit.source: Always.
trans-unit.target: 始终。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets the number of items in the session-state collection.
trans-unit.target: 当在派生类中重写时，获取会话状态集合中的项数。

trans-unit.source: The number of items in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 集合中项的数目。

trans-unit.source: Always.
trans-unit.target: 始终。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, returns an enumerator that can be used to read all the session-state variable names in the current session.
trans-unit.target: 在派生类中重写时，返回一个可用于读取当前会话中所有会话状态变量名称的枚举器。

trans-unit.source: An enumerator that can iterate through the variable names in the session-state collection.
trans-unit.target: 一个枚举器，它可循环访问会话状态集合中的变量名称。

trans-unit.source: Always.
trans-unit.target: 始终。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets a value that indicates whether the session ID is embedded in the URL.
trans-unit.target: 在派生类中重写时，获取一个值，该值指示是否在 URL 中嵌入会话 ID。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the session ID is embedded in the URL; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果会话 ID 嵌入在 URL 中，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Always.
trans-unit.target: 始终。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets a value that indicates whether the session was created during the current request.
trans-unit.target: 在派生类中重写时，获取一个值，该值指示会话是否是在当前请求过程中创建的。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the session was created during the current request; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果会话是在当前请求过程中创建的，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Always.
trans-unit.target: 始终。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets a value that indicates whether the session is read-only.
trans-unit.target: 当在派生类中重写时，获取一个值，该值指示会话是否为只读。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the session is read-only; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果会话为只读，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Always.
trans-unit.target: 始终。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets a value that indicates whether access to the collection of session-state values is synchronized (thread safe).
trans-unit.target: 在派生类中重写时，获取一个值，该值指示对会话状态值的集合的访问是否同步（线程安全）。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if access to the collection is synchronized (thread safe); otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果对该集合的访问是同步的（线程安全），则为 <see langword="true" />；否则，为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Always.
trans-unit.target: 始终。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets or sets individual session values.
trans-unit.target: 在派生类中重写时，获取或设置单个会话值。

trans-unit.source: The index of the session value.
trans-unit.target: 会话值的索引。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets or sets a session value by using the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 当在派生类中被重写时，通过使用指定的索引获取或设置一个会话值。

trans-unit.source: The session-state value that is stored at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 存储在指定的索引上的会话状态值。

trans-unit.source: Always.
trans-unit.target: 始终。

trans-unit.source: The key name of the session value.
trans-unit.target: 会话值的键名称。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets or sets a session value by using the specified name.
trans-unit.target: 在派生类中重写时，使用指定的名称获取或设置一个会话值。

trans-unit.source: The session-state value that has the specified name, or <see langword="null" /> if the item does not exist.
trans-unit.target: 具有指定名称的会话状态值，如果该项不存在，则为 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: Always.
trans-unit.target: 始终。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets a collection of the keys for all values that are stored in the session-state collection.
trans-unit.target: 当在派生类中被重写时，获取存储在会话状态集合中的所有值的密钥的集合。

trans-unit.source: The session keys.
trans-unit.target: 会话密钥。

trans-unit.source: Always.
trans-unit.target: 始终。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets or sets the locale identifier (LCID) of the current session.
trans-unit.target: 在派生类中重写时，获取或设置当前会话的区域设置标识符 (LCID)。

trans-unit.source: The LCID (culture) of the current session.
trans-unit.target: 当前会话的 LCID（区域性）。

trans-unit.source: Always.
trans-unit.target: 始终。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets the current session-state mode.
trans-unit.target: 当在派生类中重写时，获取当前会话状态模式。

trans-unit.source: The session-state mode.
trans-unit.target: 会话状态模式。

trans-unit.source: Always.
trans-unit.target: 始终。

trans-unit.source: The name of the item to delete from the session-state collection.
trans-unit.target: 要从会话状态集合中删除的项的名称。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, deletes an item from the session-state collection.
trans-unit.target: 在派生类中重写时，删除会话状态集合中的项。

trans-unit.source: Always.
trans-unit.target: 始终。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, removes all keys and values from the session-state collection.
trans-unit.target: 在派生类中重写时，从会话状态集合中移除所有键和值。

trans-unit.source: This method performs the same function as the <xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateBase.Clear%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 此方法执行相同的功能<xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateBase.Clear%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: Always.
trans-unit.target: 始终。

trans-unit.source: The index of the item to remove from the session-state collection.
trans-unit.target: 要从会话状态集合中删除的项的索引。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, deletes the item at the specified index from the session-state collection.
trans-unit.target: 在派生类中重写时，从会话状态集合中删除位于指定索引处的项。

trans-unit.source: Always.
trans-unit.target: 始终。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets the unique identifier for the session.
trans-unit.target: 在派生类中重写时，获取会话的唯一标识符。

trans-unit.source: The unique session identifier.
trans-unit.target: 会话的唯一标识符。

trans-unit.source: Always.
trans-unit.target: 始终。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets a collection of objects that are declared by <see langword="object" /> elements that are marked as server controls and scoped to the current session in the application's Global.asax file.
trans-unit.target: 在派生类中重写时，获取由 <see langword="object" /> 元素声明的对象的集合，这些元素在应用程序的 Global.asax 文件中标记为服务器控件且范围限定为当前会话。

trans-unit.source: The objects that are declared in the Global.asax file.
trans-unit.target: 在 Global.asax 文件中声明的对象。

trans-unit.source: Always.
trans-unit.target: 始终。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets an object that can be used to synchronize access to the collection of session-state values.
trans-unit.target: 在派生类中重写时，获取一个对象，该对象可用于同步对会话状态值集合的访问。

trans-unit.source: An object that can be used to synchronize access to the collection.
trans-unit.target: 可用于同步集合访问的对象。

trans-unit.source: Always.
trans-unit.target: 始终。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets or sets the time, in minutes, that can elapse between requests before the session-state provider ends the session.
trans-unit.target: 在派生类中重写时，获取和设置在会话状态提供程序结束会话之前在请求之间所允许间隔的时间量（以分钟为单位）。

trans-unit.source: The time-out period, in minutes.
trans-unit.target: 超时时间（以分钟为单位）。

trans-unit.source: Always.
trans-unit.target: 始终。
